  <div style="background: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
    <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> English-only subtitles are the <strong>worst</strong> option for language learning. Your brain defaults to reading English and ignores the Chinese audio. Always include Chinese characters in your subtitles, even if you also have English.
